  "description": {
    "zh": "我看了你之前带来的那台笔记本，内容相当炸裂，但不是我们目前的重点。不过其余的东西……\n倒正是我们要的。有的内容太敏感，等之后我们再谈。\n\n那现在我有个主意：想要容易打上鱼得先“打窝”的道理你懂吧？老套路，海岸线这么多人，我们伪装一下栽赃一下你猜到时候能不能炸出一堆鱼？应该算是个计划吧？\n\n我已经有目标了，Sanitar和他那帮人一直在惹事，是时候给他们也添点麻烦了。\n\n这活有点风险，你得伪装成上次干掉我小队的那伙人。我会给你一份装备清单，也会借你几件东西，但别想着丢了还能来要。\n\n干掉点Scav不难，顺便也要收拾几个PMC和污水厂那边的USEC游荡者。得让风声传出去。但无论如何，Sanitar和他手下一个都不能碰，听明白了吗？\n任务完成后来向我汇报。\n\n指定装备：\n - Team Wendy EXFIL防弹头盔\n - Ars Arma CPC MOD.1 插板胸挂 或 Ars Arma A18 Skanda插板胸挂\n - 任意 9x39mm 口径的武器\n - 任意 提花头巾",
    "en": "I looked through the laptop you brought to me recently, I found all sorts of crazy stuff, not something we require at the moment however. The rest of it tho...\nExactly what we need. Some of it might be too confidental, so maybe we can talk about that another time. I think I know what we could do to cause these people some damage, if we blame their crimes on someone else, the person who gets blamed will likely try to fight them back.\nSounds like a plan yeah?\n\nI already have an idea who we can put the blame on, Sanitar and his gang have been causing us enough trouble in the past. Why don't we cause them trouble too?\n\nThis will be a risky move, you will need to dress up like the operators that wiped out my group last time, I can write you down the specific things you will need, and I will lend you a few pieces of course but don't expect more when you lose it.\n\nDrop some bandits, shouldn't be a problem for you, and don't forget to wipe out a few normal operators aswell as the ex USECs from the water treatment plant. Gotta make sure that word gets around. And you can't hurt Sanitar or his men, under any circumstance, is that clear?\nReport back to me when you're done.\n\nSpecified Gear :\n - Team Wendy EXFIL Ballistic Helmet\n - Ars Arma CPC MOD.1 Plate Carrier or Ars Arma A18 Skanda Plate Carrier\n - Any Weapon chambered in 9x39mm\n - Any Shemagh"
  },
